caption.p: The effect of different concentrations of glucose on SH-SY5Y cell viability. Detection of cell viability was performed using 3-(4,5-Dimethylthiazol-2-yl)-2,5-diphenyltetrazolium bromide tetrazolium (MTT) assay. Data are presented as the means Â± SD, * p < 0.05 vs. control. p values of 200 mM glucose-treated group was 0.000.
